{
  "stem": "21527.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they also used to bring in their lunches wrapped in newspapers, which they sold to my uncle, who really wanted to know what was going on in the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Although the papers were printed in German, and it was a very one-sided sort of reporting, but at least he could read between the lines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because-- but if you were caught with a newspaper you could be shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he was a terrific risk taker, but he just had this obsession that he wanted to know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now eventually, the population of this camp grew to 4,000.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there were a lot of women and some children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And again, the same process started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One day a search party came to take all the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was hidden under a mattress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And fortunately, they didn't find me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So that's another miracle of my survival.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Germans eventually-- or the Jewish people in the ghetto, in the camp, built a small hospital as surgery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And behind the surgery a tiny little room where the, the people that had arrived in the meantime, there were a few other doctors.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all the doctors and their families slept and lived in this tiny little room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we actually didn't have to live in the general barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our own quarters, which was-- they were cramped and they were dirty and everything, but at least was our quarters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how we, we lived till, till our liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did you do in the camp?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I helped-- I helped a little bit in the surgery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I probably cleaned and did things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
